PercentMobile
=============

This plugin handles the percentmobile tracking of your Ruby on Rails website.


Example
=======

After installing put the following code in the views you want to track

<%=percent_mobile_track(REPLACE_THAT_WITH_YOUR_ASSIGNED_ID)%>

If you need custom named URL's like home or news add a second parameter:

<%=percent_mobile_track(REPLACE_THAT_WITH_YOUR_ASSIGNED_ID,'YOUR CUSTOM URL NAME')%>		


